# Grep Voice - Embedded API Keys
#
# These keys are baked into the build at compile time.
# Voice features will work out-of-the-box without user configuration.
# Users can still override with their own keys in Settings.
#
# To use:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.production
# 2. Add your actual API keys below
# 3. Rebuild the application
#
# IMPORTANT: .env.production is gitignored - never commit actual keys!

# OpenAI API Key - Required for speech-to-text (Realtime API)
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
EMBEDDED_OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ElevenLabs API Key - Required for text-to-speech
# Get your key at: https://elevenlabs.io/app/settings/api-keys
EMBEDDED_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
